    • Constructor Detail

      • StateArrayTracer

        public StateArrayTracer(AbstractArraySorter sorter,
                long millis,
                boolean toolbar)
        Creates a new instance of StateArrayTracer that will be able to display arrays.
        Parameters:
        millis - the time you want to sorting thread to wait between each iteration of the algorithm; 25L is a good one.
        toolbar - if you want to display a simple toolbar with a start button wich can start the sorting algorithms.
        sorter - the sorter to display.
